title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Russo/Thielen/Zucker/Walz
description: It's another Vox In The Box show live from the Xcel Energy Center penalty box! Michael Russo from The Athletic stops by, Vikings WR Adam Thielen talks football and hockey, Jason Zucker shoots a puck through the hole and Wes Walz shares his hockey insight!
